.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-COUNT-ACTIVE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-count-active \- FEAT-2875 channel-count-active
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-count-active
.SH DESCRIPTION
Count of active (CHANNELD_NORMAL + peer connected) channels (FEAT-2875).
.PP
Queries all peer channels via lightning-cli listpeerchannels and counts those
in state CHANNELD_NORMAL with peer_connected true.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
